edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline

Class AnnotatorImplementations

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.AnnotatorImplementations
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServerAnnotatorImplementations

    public class AnnotatorImplementations
extends Object
    A class abstracting the implementation of various annotators. Importantly, subclasses of this class can overwrite the implementation of these annotators by returning a different annotator, and StanfordCoreNLP will automatically load the new annotator instead.
    Author:
    Gabor Angeli
